    --
    Note: saves states with 3-second delay
    Note: demonstrates undo/rollback
}

Editor --> Memento : creates
History o-- Memento : stores
Runner --> Editor : uses
Runner --> History : uses

note right of Runner
Between saved states,
Runner uses a 3-second pause
to show different timestamps
for each Memento.
end note

@enduml

